@136 = ~Masterbelt~
@137 = ~The pouches of this belt hold an array of masterfully crafted tools that are most commonly used by locksmiths and watchmakers. However, such items can easily be abused for nefarious purposes, making these items a very popular accessory among thieves. This particular belt has the letter "G" engraved upon its buckle.

