@140 = ~Cowl of Acuity~
@141 = ~Once a valued property of the Xanathar Thieves Guild, this seemingly plain-looking cowl has been treated with magic in order to enhance the acumen and perception of anyone who wears it. The cowl was temporarily lost during a raid on one of the Xanathar slave-trading houses in Skullport, but recently, it re-surfaced in Calimport and made its way to Athkatla on one of the many trading caravans belonging to the Sybarr mercantile company.

